01:20:49,040 --> 01:20:53,360
'You cannot do anything to the 
Dragon if he is in the water,'  

731
01:20:53,360 --> 01:20:58,320
said the young priest, still crying. 
'And next time he will eat me!

732
01:20:59,440 --> 01:21:04,800
'You are hopeless! Hopeless!' 
shouted Monkey, angrier than ever.  

733
01:21:05,520 --> 01:21:09,200
'Do you want to sit there 
staring at the luggage forever?'

734
01:21:10,480 --> 01:21:17,280
He was still shouting angrily when the voices 
of Gods were heard in the sky. 'Monkey,  

735
