picked up his cudgel and walked down to the river.

741
01:21:52,480 --> 01:21:58,320
'You demon fish, return my horse 
to me,' he called into the water.

742
01:21:59,520 --> 01:22:06,880
The Dragon leapt out of the river. 'Who is 
