up and down until the Dragon began to feel 
weak. With a quick turn of his long tail,  

747
01:22:37,760 --> 01:22:43,440
he disappeared back into the river. Monkey 
shouted for him to come back and fight,  

748
01:22:44,000 --> 01:22:50,000
but the Dragon did not listen. Monkey 
decided to go back and tell Tripitaka.

749
01:22:51,360 --> 01:22:56,480
When Monkey returned, Tripitaka said 
something that Monkey did not like.  

750
01:22:58,800 --> 01:23:04,240
'The other day, after you fought the tiger, 
you said you could also kill dragons.  

751
01:23:05,040 --> 01:23:09,280
I do not understand why you are having 
such difficulties with this dragon.'

752
01:23:10,240 --> 01:23:15,520
'Not another word!' he cried. 'I 
will soon show you who is master!'

753
01:23:16,480 --> 01:23:22,960
Annoyed, Monkey went back to the river 
and used his magic to make a storm. The  

