grass. Beating the grass with his cudgel,  

761
01:24:05,280 --> 01:24:10,640
Monkey danced around wildly, trying 
to find him. But it was impossible.  

762
01:24:11,600 --> 01:24:16,320
So Monkey returned to Tripitaka, who 
was feeling quite sorry for himself.

763
01:24:17,520 --> 01:24:23,280
'I will be dead from cold or hunger before 
we get across this river,' said Tripitaka.

764
01:24:24,880 --> 01:24:27,680
Monkey danced and jumped and leapt in anger,  

765
01:24:28,480 --> 01:24:36,560
but finally he had to ask the Goddess Kuan-yin 
for help. When he saw her, he became angry again.

766
01:24:37,520 --> 01:24:43,840
'You told me to look after this priest,' shouted 
Monkey. 'So why did you give him a cap that I  

